definition: to carry/to convey/to load/to hold/to fill up/and/also/as well as/simultaneously
to record in writing/to carry (i.e. publish in a newspaper etc)/Taiwan pr. [zai4]/year
to return from a rewarding journey

sentences.english: Waiting for a fight, waiting for a rewarding experience of the attack.
sentences.chinese: 等待着一場戰鬥，等待着一次滿載而歸的出擊。

sentences.english: Swiftly fly the years, one season following another . Laden with happiness and tear .
sentences.chinese: 日月如梭，季節變換，滿載着歡樂和淚水。

sentences.english: May you bring love, and may you bring happiness;
sentences.chinese: 你將滿載愛和懽樂而掃。

sentences.english: The universe is very big, let fly, loaded with joy, return.
sentences.chinese: 宇宙很大，任飛翔，滿載歡樂，回航。

sentences.english: Take my word for it that driving sheep is like pushing a loaded supermarket trolley.
sentences.chinese: 我可以保證，趕羊就像推一輛滿載的超市購物車。

sentences.english: SOHO everything, full of hope, full of joy.
sentences.chinese: 蘇荷的一切，充滿期待，滿載歡樂。

sentences.english: At intervals along the road we ran into mule-cart convoys carrying mountain products to the plains below.
sentences.chinese: 一路上我們遇到一隊隊滿載山貨下平原去的騾車。

sentences.english: A wagon loaded with asters heads for the local market.
sentences.chinese: 一輛滿載着紫菀花的馬車駛往當地的市場。

sentences.english: You, in the full I miss the days, quietly left.
sentences.chinese: 你，在這滿載我思戀的日子裏，悄悄地走了。

sentences.english: The interpreter of the caravan answered that we had come from the island of Syria with much merchandise.
sentences.chinese: 商隊的翻譯答道我們滿載着商貨自敘利亞的島嶼而來。

sentences.english: A pair of Oxen was drawing a heavily loaded wagon along a miry country road.
sentences.chinese: 有兩隻公牛拉着一輛滿載的貨車走在鄉間泥濘的路上。

sentences.english: The ship was part of a treasure fleet.
sentences.chinese: 這支船屬於一個滿載着寶物的艦隊。

sentences.english: A worker bee's head has two antennae loaded with 3, 000 sensory organs.
sentences.chinese: 工蜂的頭上有兩根滿載3000個感覺器官的觸鬚。

sentences.english: The boat full of passengers was set adrift.
sentences.chinese: 滿載旅客的船被漂走了。

sentences.english: Integrating business and leisure tours, we will ensure you a rewarding journey in Jiaxing.
sentences.chinese: 集休閒與商務一體的嘉興之旅，相信會讓你滿載而歸。

sentences.english: The turbine had been running for 4 hours beforecarrying a full load.
sentences.chinese: 透平在滿載前已運轉了4個小時。
